It’s TMI time! I wanted to share a more personal side of me with you guys and shed some light on my journey with @naturalcycles . I would like to preface this by saying this is what has worked for me, this was my personal choice, and everyone has different cycles. I am sharing this in hopes that this will help one of you as much as it has helped me.

With that said, I have not been on an oral contraceptive for roughly 5 years now, and to be completely candid, it did not agree with me.

Within the last year I began using the Natural Cycles app, which is the first FDA cleared birth control app (it’s been FDA cleared since 2018!). NC° uses an algorithm that analyzes hormone-driven changes in body temperature to let you know when you’re fertile (red day) or not fertile (green day), so you can prevent or plan pregnancy naturally. All you have to do is measure your temp (with a thermometer, Oura Ring, or Apple Watch w/temp sensors) and then check your fertility status in the NC° app. It’s backed by science and research and is proven to be 98% effective with perfect use (perfect use = no unprotected sex on red days) and 93% effective with typical use.

Try it out for yourselves using my code “KAITY” at Naturalcycles.com for 15% off your first annual subscription + a free thermometer 

Natural Cycles is for 18+ and does not protect against STIs AD
